column2: select top # a.eid,a.Which_eye_s_affected_by_myopia_short_sight__#,b.Age_at_recruitment_#, b.Ethnic_background_#,c.meaning AS &&&  from dbo.Eyesight a      cross apply openjson(Which_eye_s_affected_by_myopia_short_sight__#) j join dbo.Baseline_characteristics b on a.eid=b.eid join metadata.columns d on d.column_name =&&& AND d.table_name=&&& join metadata.encoding c on c.encoding_id=d.encoding_id AND c.value=b.Sex_#  where j.value is not Null
